<div class = ""card-panel hoverable""><p class=AAE-Normal dir=LTR>To assemble the device, you must first install the
back panel on the case. Stand the case in front of you, in a way that the power
socket is on your right side. Connect one of the earth wires to the power
socket and the other one to the earth socket.</p></div>

