dir=LTR></span>Placing the amplifier module in the case</h3>

<div class = ""card-panel hoverable""><p class=AAE-Normal dir=LTR>The amplifier module is placed into the case where
the racks are less spaced (opposite to the input power socket).</p></div>

<div><p class=AAA-Aks dir=LTR style='text-align:center;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:
embed'>
 <center><img class=""Image_Page""  src=""../../../../Images/Tester/Assemblying_Stages_of_AMT105_Tester_files/image014.png""");
