mso-bidi-theme-font:major-latin;color:black;font-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-style:
normal;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none'><span ></span></span><![endif]><span dir=LTR></span>Position of amplifier module
inside the case</h4>

<div class = ""card-panel hoverable""><p class=AAE-Normal dir=LTR>The complete side of the amplifier goes to the case
wall. The edges of the module should be placed inside the 4 racks.</p></div>

