none;text-underline:none'><span ></span></span><![endif]><span
dir=LTR></span>Connecting the socket of fan to the amplifier module</h3>

<div class = ""card-panel hoverable""><p class=AAE-Normal dir=LTR>Insert the module up to 5 cm to the end of the
